data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home nestled in Conewago Township, Northeastern School district, offering comfortable living and serene surroundings.  This inviting 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence boasts a versatile layout designed for ease and functionality. The master bedroom features an attached room that offers endless possibilities—it could serve as a nursery, a cozy office space, or a luxurious walk-in closet, allowing for tailored use to suit your lifestyle.  Situated on a generous .45-acre lot, the property provides a picturesque backdrop with its peaceful setting backing up to a sprawling farm field. Imagine waking up to the tranquility of rural vistas right outside your window.  Inside, the home offers an unfinished basement with ample storage space, providing the opportunity for customization and expansion to suit your needs and preferences.  Adding to the comfort and convenience, a brand-new central A/C system ensures a pleasant climate year-round.  Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a cozy family home, this property offers a perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and natural beauty. Don't miss the chance to make this delightful residence your own!
